 Pod ‡¶Æ‡ßç‡¶Ø‡¶æ‡¶®‡ßá‡¶ú‡¶Æ‡ßç‡¶Ø‡ßá‡¶®‡ßç‡¶ü:

* Create Pod: kubectl run [pod_name] --image=[image_name]
- ‡¶Æ‡ßç‡¶Ø‡¶æ‡¶®‡¶∂‡¶® ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡¶æ ‡¶®‡¶æ‡¶Æ ‡¶è‡¶¨‡¶Ç ‡¶á‡¶Æ‡ßá‡¶ú ‡¶¶‡¶ø‡¶Ø‡¶º‡ßá ‡¶®‡¶§‡ßÅ‡¶® Pod ‡¶§‡ßà‡¶∞‡¶ø ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡ßá‡•§

* Expose Pod: kubectl expose pod [pod_name] --port=[external_port] --target-port=[container_port]
- ‡¶¨‡¶≤‡ßá ‡¶¶‡ßá‡¶ì‡¶Ø‡¶º‡¶æ Port ‡¶è ‡¶ï‡¶®‡ßç‡¶ü‡ßá‡¶á‡¶®‡¶æ‡¶∞‡¶ü‡¶ø ‡¶è‡¶ï‡ßç‡¶∏‡¶™‡ßã‡¶∏ ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡ßá‡•§

* Execute Command in Pod: kubectl exec [pod_name] -- [command]
- Pod ‡¶è‡¶∞ ‡¶≠‡¶ø‡¶§‡¶∞ ‡¶ï‡ßã‡¶® ‡¶ï‡¶Æ‡¶æ‡¶®‡ßç‡¶° ‡¶ö‡¶æ‡¶≤‡¶æ‡¶®‡ßã‡¶∞ ‡¶ú‡¶®‡ßç‡¶Ø ‡¶¨‡ßç‡¶Ø‡¶¨‡¶π‡ßÉ‡¶§ ‡¶π‡¶Ø‡¶º ‡¶è‡¶á ‡¶ï‡¶Æ‡¶æ‡¶®‡ßç‡¶°‡•§

Deployment and Scaling:

* Create Deployment: kubectl create deployment [name] --image=[image]
- ‡¶ï‡¶Æ‡¶æ‡¶®‡ßç‡¶°‡ßá ‡¶¶‡ßá‡¶ì‡¶Ø‡¶º‡¶æ ‡¶á‡¶Æ‡ßá‡¶ú ‡¶•‡ßá‡¶ï‡ßá ‡¶è‡¶ï‡¶ü‡¶ø Deployment ‡¶§‡ßà‡¶∞‡¶ø ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡ßá‡•§

* Scale Deployment: kubectl scale deployment [name] --replicas=[n]
- Deployment ‡¶ï‡ßá scale ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡ßá ‡¶∞‡ßá‡¶™‡ßç‡¶≤‡¶ø‡¶ï‡¶æ‡¶§‡ßá ‡¶¨‡¶≤‡ßá ‡¶¶‡ßá‡¶ì‡¶Ø‡¶º‡¶æ ‡¶®‡¶æ‡¶Æ‡ßç‡¶¨‡¶æ‡¶∞ ‡¶™‡¶∞‡ßç‡¶Ø‡¶®‡ßç‡¶§‡•§

* Update Deployment: kubectl set image deployment/[name] [container_name]=[new_image]
- Deployment ‡¶è‡¶∞ ‡¶≠‡¶ø‡¶§‡¶∞‡ßá‡¶∞ ‡¶ï‡¶®‡ßç‡¶ü‡ßá‡¶á‡¶®‡¶æ‡¶∞‡ßá‡¶∞ ‡¶á‡¶Æ‡ßá‡¶ú ‡¶∏‡ßá‡¶ü ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡ßá ‡¶¶‡ßá‡¶Ø‡¶º‡•§

Namespaces and Contexts:

* List Namespaces: kubectl get namespaces
- Cluster ‡¶Æ‡¶ß‡ßç‡¶Ø‡¶ï‡¶æ‡¶∞ ‡¶∏‡¶ï‡¶≤ namespaces ‡¶¶‡ßá‡¶ñ‡¶æ‡¶Ø‡¶º‡•§

* Switch Namespace: kubectl config set-context --current --namespace=[name]
- Cluster ‡¶è‡¶∞ ‡¶≠‡¶ø‡¶§‡¶∞ ‡¶Ö‡¶®‡ßç‡¶Ø namespace ‡¶è ‡¶Ø‡¶æ‡¶ì‡¶Ø‡¶º‡¶æ‡¶∞ ‡¶ú‡¶®‡ßç‡¶Ø‡•§

* Set Default Namespace: kubectl config set-context $(kubectl config current-context) --namespace=[namespace]
- ‡¶°‡¶ø‡¶´‡¶≤‡ßç‡¶ü namespace ‡¶∏‡ßá‡¶ü ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡ßá ‡¶¨‡¶∞‡ßç‡¶§‡¶Æ‡¶æ‡¶® Context ‡¶è‡¶∞ ‡¶ú‡¶®‡ßç‡¶Ø‡•§

